---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { ArrowLeft, ArrowRight } from "@lucide/astro";
import p1 from "../../assets/template-2/person-1.png";
import p2 from "../../assets/template-2/person-2.png";
import p3 from "../../assets/template-2/hero-student.png";
---

<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials-2 section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonials-header flex">
      <h2>What everyone says</h2>
      <div class="carousel-controls">
        <button class="control-btn"><ArrowLeft /></button>
        <button class="control-btn active"><ArrowRight /></button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p>Lacus vestibulum ultricies mi risus, duis non, volutpat nullam non. Magna congue eros faucibus sed aliquet ac sed consectetur. Libero sem nisl vitae, placerat donec aliquam dui, habitant rhoncus.</p>
        <div class="user-meta">
          <Image src={p1} alt="User" class="avatar" />
          <div>
            <h4>Helen Jimmy</h4>
            <span>Financial Director</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p>Odio rhoncus ornare ut quam. Adipiscing sed duis eget scelerisque id. In feugiat fucid enim sagittis adivina nisl, nec taciti. Facilitasis, ultrices ultrices neque, leo ultrices nisl.</p>
        <div class="user-meta">
          <Image src={p2} alt="User" class="avatar" />
          <div>
            <h4>Ralph Edwards</h4>
            <span>Math Teacher</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <p>Sagittis nam egestas ut ac malesuada proin risus. Morbi proin id nisl aliquam. Diam tellus, amet nec imperdiet. Neque in volutpat tellus, congue malesuada et nisl tellus s.</p>
        <div class="user-meta">
          <Image src={p3} alt="User" class="avatar" />
          <div>
            <h4>Hellena John</h4>
            <span>Psychology Student</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-2 {
    background: #fdfdfd;
  }

  .testimonials-header {
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .testimonials-header h2 {
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .carousel-controls {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .control-btn {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    background: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.3s ease;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .control-btn.active {
    background: var(--color-primary, #52BD94);
    border-color: var(--color-primary, #52BD94);
    color: white;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #4a4a4a;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .user-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .user-meta h4 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .user-meta span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #999;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .testimonials-header h2 { font-size: 36px; }
  }
</style>
